United States Oil Co said Dr. V. diGuevara Suardo Fabbri was appointed president and chiefexeuctive, effective October 31, replacing William Rueckert,who will resign on that date.    Rueckert told Reuters he resigned to puruse other businessactivities.    Last November, Fabbri bought a controlling interest in thecompany and has since brought in his own management.    The company said that three new directors have been electedand that one present director resigned effective October 16. Reuter&#3;